'''Anthony Matumba''' is a South African politician who has been a [[Member of the National Assembly of South Africa]] since January 2022. A member of the [[Economic Freedom Fighters]], he serves on the party's Central Command Team, its highest decision-making structure. He is a former [[Makhado Local Municipality]] councillor.

==Political career==
Matumba ke leloko la mokgatlo wa Balwela Tokologo ya Ekonomi (EFF). Ka ngwaga wa 2016, o ile a kgethwa bjalo ka mokhanselara wa EFF ka Mmasepaleng wa Selegae wa Makhado ka [[Limpopo]]. O kgethilwe bjalo ka leloko la tlaleletšo la sebopego sa Sehlopha sa Taelo ya Bogare sa EFF, e lego sebopego sa godimo sa go tšea diphetho sa mokgatlo magareng ga dikhonferense, ka khonferenseng ya go kgetha ya EFF ka Dibatsela 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|last=Cele|first=S’thembile|title=EFF elects 40-member central command team|url=https://www.news24.com/citypress/news/eff-elects-40-member-central-command-team-20191215|access-date=2022-01-28|website=Citypress|language=en-US}}</ref>

Ka Phupu 2020, dinyakišišo tša Digital Forensic Lab (DFRLab) di kgokaganya akhaonto ya Tracy Zille [[Twitter]] ya go swara morafe yeo e šomišitšwego go phatlalatša diteng tša go nyatša le tša kgethollo ya semorafe le go tlaiša basadi ba bathobaso go Matumba<ref>{{Cite web|title=EFF central command team member linked to race-baiting Tracy Zille account|url=https://www.iol.co.za/news/politics/eff-central-command-team-member-linked-to-race-baiting-tracy-zille-account-50799868|access-date=2022-01-28|website=www.iol.co.za|language=en}}</ref> Go utolotšwe gape gore Matumba o be a hwetša letseno go tšwa go go dira ditshwayotshwayo tša lehloyo go Twitter ka dikhamphani tšeo a bego a na le tšona le go di ngwadiša tšeo badiriši ba Twitter ba bego ba lebišitšwe go tšona. Matumba o latoditse gore o hlokometse akhaonto ya Twitter..<ref>{{Cite web|title=#TracyZille outed as front for EFF-aligned local government official — Lies, he says|url=https://www.timeslive.co.za/news/south-africa/2020-07-10-tracyzille-outed-as-front-for-eff-aligned-local-government-official-lies-he-says/|access-date=2022-01-28|website=TimesLIVE|language=en-ZA}}</ref> Ke moka [[South African Human Rights Commission]] (SAHRC) e ile ya iša Matumba Kgorong ya Tsheko ya Tekatekano ka morago ga gore e hwetše ngongorego go tšwa go leloko la setšhaba. Molato wo o theeleditšwe kgorong ya tsheko ka la 27 Phupu 2021, .<ref>{{Cite web|last=|url=https://www.timeslive.co.za/news/south-africa/2021-07-27-eff-councillor-in-court-over-racist-tracy-zille-tweets/|title=EFF councillor in court over racist 'Tracy Zille' tweets|access-date=2022-01-28|website=TimesLIVE|language=en-ZA}}</ref> gomme ya bušetšwa morago go Phato 2021 ka la 29 Phupu.<ref>{{Cite web|title=Case against EFF councillor allegedly behind controversial @TracyZille account postponed|url=https://www.timeslive.co.za/news/south-africa/2021-07-29-case-against-eff-councillor-allegedly-behind-controversial-tracyzille-account-postponed/|access-date=2022-01-28|website=TimesLIVE|language=en-ZA}}</ref>

=== Parliament ===
Molato wa Kgorotsheko ya Tekatekano o be o beakantšwe go tšwela pele ka la 26 Pherekgong 2022, eupša o ile wa bušetšwa morago go dumelela Matumba go ikana bjalo ka Leloko la EFF la Seboka sa Maloko a Palamente.<ref>{{Cite web|last=Belinda Pheto|title=EFF member alleged to be behind fake #TracyZille account to be sworn in as MP today|url=https://www.dispatchlive.co.za/politics/2022-01-26-eff-member-alleged-to-be-behind-fake-tracyzille-account-to-be-sworn-in-as-mp-today/|access-date=2022-01-28|website=DispatchLIVE|language=en-ZA}}</ref> Moletlo wa go ikana o be o okametšwe ke Sepikara Nosiviwe Mapisa-Nqakula..<ref>{{Cite web|last=Felix|first=Jason|title=EFF councillor accused of using fake 'Tracy Zille' account sworn in as MP|url=https://www.news24.com/news24/southafrica/news/just-in-eff-councillor-accused-of-using-fake-tracey-zille-account-sworn-in-as-mp-20220126|access-date=2022-01-28|website=News24|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Dayimani|first=Malibongwe|title=EFF member accused of using fake 'Tracy Zille' Twitter account to be sworn in as an MP|url=https://www.news24.com/news24/southafrica/news/eff-member-accused-of-using-fake-tracy-zille-twitter-account-to-be-sworn-in-as-an-mp-20220126|access-date=2022-01-28|website=News24|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=EFF member behind fake account sworn in as party MP|url=https://www.iol.co.za/news/politics/eff-member-behind-fake-account-sworn-in-as-party-mp-ccbe711e-9f0a-482f-9f0e-2f76bbd26cd5|access-date=2022-01-28|website=www.iol.co.za|language=en}}</ref>

